{
  "stem": "6258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well-- but it was not even that they were menial, and that people were being beaten there, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, we had to go and work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was in that-- barracks-- in SS barracks, Gestapo, well, soldiers, Luftwaffe, and so forth, all over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually, I had to go, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents first didn't wanted to, because they knew, for heaven's sake, what we are going to do there-- you will scrub the floors, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- but the one thing what was good for us, for Jewish girls, that the German soldiers were afraid of rassenschande.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was said that the rassenschande, so therefore, they-- they were not after us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, what was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Could you define the term?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rassenschande-- it was thought that when Jewish soldiers-- when a German soldier is having something to do with a Jewish woman, then he brings shame for his Aryan race-- race.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And therefore, it was said that, therefore, they were afraid of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were left in peace, at least about this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But still, this was very hard physical work, doing all this dragging coal, or heavy things, scrubbing floors, endless row of windows to be cleaned.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And practically, shortly, the ghetto changed into a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were being taken in the morning out of the ghetto with-- to different places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were coming in the evening-- there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But at least it was still something like a home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At least we still were together with my parents, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then, it was another in October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was another very ruthless thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there in in this film, there is shown this courtyard where they throw all the furniture out, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
